'''Turpu Kapu''' is a [[Telugu language|Telugu]] term for a sub-caste of [[Kapu]] living on the eastern (''[[turpu]]'') frontier of [[Andhra Pradesh]].The term ''kapu'' means "protector" in the [[Telugu language]]. 

